            <chapter title="15.3.1 Depth-First Search for Digraph" id="15-3-1-depth-first-search-for-digraph">
                <note>
                    <p>Every undirected graph is a digraph (with edges in both
                        directions).</p>
                    <p>DFS is a <format color="OrangeRed">digraph</format> algorithm, same method as for undirected
